<br>
1: press the &quot;jump to imageready&quot; button at the botom of the tool bar.<br>
<br>
If you dont hvae the &quot;animation&quot; bar open go to Windows-&gt;animation. and press the dublicate button(looks like &quot;new layer button&quot;)<br>
